@startuml IBM_logdna-cos
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

rectangle "IBM CIS" as CIS
rectangle "IBM COS\n(Source Bucket)" as COS_Source
rectangle "Serverless\nFunction" as Function
rectangle "IBM LogDNA" as LogDNA
rectangle "IBM COS\n(Archive Bucket)" as COS_Archive

CIS --> COS_Source : Logpush\n(Zipped JSON Logs)
COS_Source --> Function : Object Created\nEvent Trigger
Function --> COS_Source : Download Log File
Function --> Function : Unzip & Parse Logs
Function --> LogDNA : Send Logs in Batches\n(5000 logs per batch)
Function --> COS_Archive : Archive Processed Logs
Function --> COS_Source : Delete Original Log File

note right of Function
  Retry Mechanism for\nLogDNA API Failures
end note
@enduml